01:03:58,401 --> 01:04:00,369
- I didn't, it's my lunch break.

1222
01:04:00,369 --> 01:04:01,504
So I can't stay long.

1223
01:04:02,405 --> 01:04:03,673
- You shouldn't be here at all.

1224
01:04:03,673 --> 01:04:04,507
- Why?

1225
01:04:05,908 --> 01:04:07,143
Why not?

1226
01:04:07,143 --> 01:04:08,377
- Because I don't
  want your pity.

1227
01:04:09,512 --> 01:04:11,147
I don't want you
 cutting up my pizza,

1228
01:04:11,147 --> 01:04:12,315
wiping my chin off.

1229
01:04:12,315 --> 01:04:13,783
I don't need it

1230
01:04:13,783 --> 01:04:16,252
- I have no intention of
 wiping off your chin Ruben.

1231
01:04:16,252 --> 01:04:18,054
And I don't feel
 sorry for you okay.

1232
01:04:20,690 --> 01:04:21,524
I'm concerned.

1233
01:04:22,658 --> 01:04:23,492
Move over.

1234
01:04:35,871 --> 01:04:38,641
What?

1235
01:04:38,641 --> 01:04:39,642
What'd I do?

1236
01:04:41,544 --> 01:04:42,378
- Nothing.

1237
01:04:45,181 --> 01:04:46,616
My mother put you up to this?

1238
01:04:46,616 --> 01:04:48,050
- Nah.

1239
01:04:48,050 --> 01:04:50,086
