 along a little bit.

1240
01:04:51,387 --> 01:04:53,689
But I was coming
 back the whole time.

1241
01:04:57,994 --> 01:04:58,828
- Good.

1242
01:05:01,897 --> 01:05:03,366
- I've known a ton of guys,

1243
01:05:03,366 --> 01:05:07,503
but nothing like you.

1244
01:05:07,503 --> 01:05:08,371
You're different.

1245
01:05:09,839 --> 01:05:10,940
- I was always here.

1246
01:05:11,841 --> 01:05:13,075
- I wasn't.

1247
01:05:13,075 --> 01:05:16,212
