 but I wasn't really.

1248
01:05:17,413 --> 01:05:18,214
- I know.

1249
01:05:19,348 --> 01:05:20,750
I know, I used to watch you.

1250
01:05:21,817 --> 01:05:23,019
- Watch me?

1251
01:05:23,019 --> 01:05:23,819
- Mm hmm.

1252
01:05:25,488 --> 01:05:26,822
I went to your farm once.

1253
01:05:28,491 --> 01:05:32,528
I guess I was 12 you
 were probably 14.

1254
01:05:33,796 --> 01:05:34,630
A woman.

1255
01:05:36,699 --> 01:05:38,801
