1258
01:05:44,106 --> 01:05:46,442
What I was gonna say,
what you were gonna say.

1259
01:05:49,078 --> 01:05:52,648
Anyway, my dad and I got there.

1260
01:05:54,150 --> 01:05:58,087
You were all dressed in
 faded overalls and pigtails.

1261
01:06:00,723 --> 01:06:03,225
And all I could do is stand
 there and look at you.

1262
01:06:05,895 --> 01:06:06,962
I was just a foot away from you

1263
01:06:06,962 --> 01:06:10,066
but the words wouldn't come.

1264
01:06:11,400 --> 01:06:13,069
I guess my dad knew
 I had a crush on you.

1265
01:06:13,069 --> 01:06:15,371
He took your grandpa,
 went into the barn.

1266
01:06:18,307 --> 01:06:19,575
I guess he thought
  if he'd leave me

1267
01:06:19,575 --> 01:06:20,676
alone long enough
  with you that I'd

1268
01:06:20,676 --> 01:06:21,877
get the nerve to speak.

1269
01:06:23,512 --> 01:06:24,347
- Did you?

1270
01:06:25,214 --> 01:06:26,082
- No.

1271
01:06:26,082 --> 01:06:27,350
- Shoot.

1272
01:06:27,350 --> 01:06:28,951
I wish you would of.

1273
01:06:28,951 --> 01:06:30,219
Then I could be different.

1274
01:06:30,219 --> 01:06:32,288
