  me become normal.

1275
01:06:35,291 --> 01:06:37,226
- Well now, why'd
  I wanna do that?

1276
01:06:38,994 --> 01:06:39,829
Hmm?

1277
01:06:42,765 --> 01:06:45,768
Why would anyone wanna
  change you Frannie Vaughn?

1278
01:07:00,149 --> 01:07:02,651
- Ruben said that you
  and my gran were friends.

1279
01:07:02,651 --> 01:07:04,353
- Best friends dear.

1280
01:07:05,521 --> 01:07:08,858
- Did she ever mention
my great great grandma?

1281
01:07:08,858 --> 01:07:09,692
- Delia.

1282
01:07:10,693 --> 01:07:11,527
- Yes.

1283
01:07:13,062 --> 01:07:14,597
What was she like?

1284
01:07:14,597 --> 01:07:17,333
- Your great great grandma Delia

1285
01:07:17,333 --> 01:07:19,268
had plenty of passion.

1286
01:07:21,036 --> 01:07:23,639
She was married to
  a good man really.

1287
01:07:23,639 --> 01:07:26,509
One day she met a man

1288
01:07:26,509 --> 01:07:28,244
who made her sick with love.

1289
01:07:29,145 --> 01:07:31,213
He promised to take her away.

1290
01:07:31,213 --> 01:07:34,450
Far away from North Carolina.

1291
01:07:34,450 --> 01:07:37,420
All the way to a farm
 he had in Kentucky.

1292
01:07:37,420 --> 01:07:40,289
She left her family
 and she and this man

1293
01:07:40,289 --> 01:07:42,758
traveled for weeks

1294
01:07:42,758 --> 01:07:45,494
until they reached
  his homestead.

1295
01:07:45,494 --> 01:07:48,497
Where she was to
 begin her new life.

1296
01:07:48,497 --> 01:07:53,235
One day Delia saw a man she'd
 known from her old home.

1297
01:07:53,235 --> 01:07:56,305
"How'd you come to be
 in Kentucky" she said.

1298
01:07:57,206 --> 01:07:59,341
"Well Delia" he said,

1299
01:07:59,341 --> 01:08:00,943
"we're nowhere near Kentucky.

1300
01:08:00,943 --> 01:08:03,112
"This is North Carolina."

1301
01:08:03,112 --> 01:08:05,080
- North Carolina?

1302
01:08:05,080 --> 01:08:10,085
- Her lover had taken her
around in circles all that time.

1303
01:08:11,420 --> 01:08:14,957
She was only seven
  miles from home.

1304
01:08:14,957 --> 01:08:16,292
She'd left him.

1305
01:08:17,293 --> 01:08:19,595
Came back here to Silk Hope.

1306
01:08:19,595 --> 01:08:20,496
- To her husband?

1307
01:08:22,364 --> 01:08:23,732
- He took her back.

1308
01:08:25,134 --> 01:08:26,669
But the community didn't.

1309
01:08:27,536 --> 01:08:30,573
They refused to forgive her.

1310
01:08:30,573 --> 01:08:33,275
Finally she had a child.

1311
01:08:33,275 --> 01:08:34,677
- Great grandma Rose.

1312
01:08:34,677 --> 01:08:36,879
- Yes, Rose.

1313
01:08:36,879 --> 01:08:38,514
When Delia's husband died,

1314
01:08:39,949 --> 01:08:42,485
community turned
 their backs on her.

1315
01:08:43,953 --> 01:08:45,421
