1316
01:08:47,156 --> 01:08:51,961
Finally she was forced to return
to the man who tricked her.

1317
01:08:53,229 --> 01:08:54,763
- I thought family
 stories were supposed

1318
01:08:54,763 --> 01:08:56,232
to have happy endings?

1319
01:08:58,000 --> 01:08:58,834
Poor Delia.

1320
01:09:05,774 --> 01:09:06,709
Hey.

1321
01:09:06,709 --> 01:09:07,543
- Hey.

1322
01:09:07,543 --> 01:09:08,544
- How ya doing today?

1323
01:09:08,544 --> 01:09:09,845
